title: iPhone's Amazing New Camera, Tesla vs Porsche Round 2, & Google Pixel 4 Leaks
description:
Today, we revisit the Tesla vs Porsche Taycan debate by dissecting some laptimes that Tesla put down on an all new Model S model available next year, followed by a deep-dive into how great the iPhone 11 cameras have performed after a week of daily use, followed by an examination of the numerous Google Pixel 4 Leaks to see what we're excited about in the upcoming phone. Lastly, we wrap it all up with another Listener Q & A!
